d a miserable existence by </div><div class="t m7ae x6e h4 y61d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">asking the pity of all that passed through. </div><div class="t m7d6 x6e h4 y65b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Such contrasts has sin introduced into this </div><div class="t m819 x6e h4 y87 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">world.&quot;-The </div><div class="t m907 x4d h30 y60a ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Pulpit Commentary, </div><div class="t m7ef x1d3 h4 y60a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Acts, </div><div class="t m6ac x6e h4 y45 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Vol. 1, </div><div class="t ma9d xac h6 y44 ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. </div><div class="t maac x9d h4 y44 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">98. </div><div class="t mc4e x2b h36 y1a22 ff2 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[101 </div><div class="t mecb x5a h36 y1a22 ff2 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
